high.title: A DNS request have been done to www.cerberusapp.com which is tagged as STALKERWARE.
high.description: The domain name www.cerberusapp.com seen in the capture has been explicitly tagged as malicious. This indicates that your device is likely compromised and needs to be investigated deeply.

low.title: HTTP communications have been done to the host www.cerberusapp.com
low.description: Your device exchanged with the host www.cerberusapp.com by using HTTP, an unencrypted protocol. Even if this behavior is not malicious by itself, it is unusual to see HTTP communications issued from smartphone applications running in the background. Please check the host reputation by searching it on the internet.
